 usecase \"Process Payment\" as UC_ProcessPayment
 usecase \"Set Recycle Prices\" as UC_SetPrices

}

Customer --> UC_SubmitRequest

Customer --> UC_ViewRequestStatus
Customer --> UC_CheckPrices
Customer --> UC_ViewPaymentHistory

Administrator --> UC_ViewAllRequests

@enduml",
